data.description: This home is truly a diamond in the ruff. With a little investment this home can reach it's true beauty. With a large kitchen open to the family room, formal dining and living rooms. With many windows this home is light and bright. The primary bedroom is on the first floor and secluded in the rear of the home for privacy. All the other bedrooms are upstairs. Located in a good area of the subdivision with easy access to Beltway 8. New industry is developing all around the area. Take the time to see this home. With a little imagination and elbow grease this home can truly shine.
